        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 7. Larval abdominal apex showing posterior disc, dorsal: (A) Dynamis borassi (Fabricius); (B) Rhynchophorus palmarum (Linnaeus). Spiracles of D. borassi (external view, not at same scale): (C) thoracic; (D) abdominal I; (E) abdominal IV. (F) Thoracic spiracle and trachea of R. palmarum, seen from inside of body. (G,H) Spiracles and tracheal system of D.borassi,seen from inside of body:thoracic,abdominal IV.Abdominal spiracleVIII:(I) D.borassi; (J)R.palmarum. Scale bars: A and B = 2 mm,C and F-H = 0.2 mm,D and E = 0.1mm,I and J = 0.5 mm." ;
